primerica’s board of directors elects beatriz r perez as a board member  business wire primerica’s board of directors elects beatriz r perez as a board member may    pm eastern daylight time duluth gabusiness wireprimerica inc nysepri today announced the election of beatriz r perez to the company’s board of directors ms perez age  has been employed by the cocacola company “cocacola” since  she has been chief sustainability officer for cocacola since july  prior to her current position ms perez held the positions of chief marketing officer for the north american division of cocacola from april  to july  senior vice president integrated marketing for the north american division of coca cola from may  to april  and vice president media sports and entertainment marketing from  to may  from  to  she held the positions of associate brand manager classic coke sports marketing and nascar manager vice president of sports and vice president of the victory junction group board ms perez also is the chair emeritus of the grammy foundation she served on the board of directors of hsbc finance corporation from may  through april  she served on the board of directors of hsbc north america from april  through april  and on the board of directors of hsbc bank nevada na from july  through april  ms perez graduated with a bs degree from the university of maryland “we are thrilled to have beatriz join our board” said d richard williams chairman of the board and coceo of primerica “she brings extensive marketing experience and a clear understanding of consumer behavior that will be very valuable to our board and management team” ms perez said “i’m pleased to join primerica’s board of directors because i believe in what they’re doing to help bring financial security to their main street clients this type of economic empowerment is helping people and families realize their potential and fulfill their dreams” about primerica inc primerica inc headquartered in duluth ga is a leading distributor of financial products to middle income households in north america primerica representatives educate their main street clients about how to better prepare for a more secure financial future by assessing their needs and providing appropriate solutions through term life insurance which we underwrite and mutual funds annuities and other financial products which we distribute primarily on behalf of third parties in addition primerica provides an entrepreneurial full or parttime business opportunity for individuals seeking to earn income by distributing the company’s financial products we insured more than  million lives and maintained approximately  million investment accounts on behalf of our clients at december   primerica stock is included in the sp midcap  and the russell  stock indices and is traded on the new york stock exchange under the symbol “pri” contacts primerica inckeith hancock keithhancockprimericacom contacts primerica inckeith hancock keithhancockprimericacom search advanced news search advanced news search log in sign up beatriz r perez executive profile  biography  bloomberg july    am et beverages company overview of the cocacola company snapshotpeople  overviewboard memberscommittees executive profile beatriz r perez senior vp and chief public affairs communications  sustainability officer  the cocacola companyagetotal calculated compensationthis person is connected to  board members in  different organizations across  different industriessee board relationships background ms beatriz r perez also known as bea has been the senior vice president and chief public affairs communications and sustainability officer of the cocacola company since may   ms perez leads a newly integrated team across public affairs and communications sustainability and global partnerships to support the cocacola companys growth model ms perez develops and leads programs on global sustainability with a focus on water stewardship and womens economic  empowerment ms perez ser